    <h4>Biography</h4>
    <div class='note'>
      <p>Matthew Garrett has been working on Linux power management for several years, and recently managed to escape fruit flies in order to focus on it full time. He now works for Red Hat with responsibility for beating on whichever part of the stack is currently responsible for sucking excessive amounts of power. He may fix your laptop if asked sufficiently nicely.</p>
